    </p>
    <h3 class="text-xl mt-8 mb-4">
      Additional Disclosures for UK General Data Protection Regulation (UK GDPR)
      Compliance (UK)
    </h3>
    <h4>Data Controller / Data Processor</h4>
    <p class="mb-2">
      The GDPR distinguishes between organisations that process personal
      information for their own purposes (known as “data controllers”) and
      organizations that process personal information on behalf of other
      organizations (known as “data processors”). For the purposes covered by
      this Privacy Policy, we are a Data Controller with respect to the personal
