      controller obligations under GDPR.
    </p>
    <h4>Third-Party Provided Content</h4>
    <p class="mb-2">
      We may indirectly collect personal information about you from
      third-parties who have your permission to share it. For example, if you
      purchase a product or service from a business working with us, and give
